
*
************* SERVER  INSTALL PROCESS FOR THE CHEMICS WEB SERVICE *********************
*

1) mkdir CHEMICSROOTDIR
2) cd CHEMICSROOTDIR
3) git archive --remote /disk1/jonsta/local/ChemicsWS --format tar master | tar xf -
4) git archive --remote /disk1/jonsta/local/ChemicsEndpoints --format tar master | tar xf - -C ChemicsEndpoints
5) rsync -a /disk1/jonsta/dev/Chemics/ChemicsModelDir 
6) Modify the ChemicsWS/ChemicsWS/startWS.sh script to define correct CHEMICSROOTPATH, port and execution settings (arguments to python ChemicsWS.py)
For production mode: ./startWS.sh $PORT  False True
7) ./startWS.sh 
